        'I want to close with something that sits underneath all of this, because I think it changes the relationship to practice design in a way that makes everything more sustainable.',
        'The four variables — challenge level, feedback loops, constraint architecture, recovery structure — are a technical framework. And frameworks are useful. But frameworks can also become another thing to be rigorous about, another way to be a high-performing practitioner who has optimized everything and is still somehow missing something.',
